<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_02_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_02_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">분수만큼 색칠하고, 크기가 같은 분수를 찾아 써 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box dir_col gap_20">
          <div class="flex align_center gap_40">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
              <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap wrap3" data-answer-single="2">
                <button type="button" class="seg1 selected"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg2"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg3"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
              <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>6</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap wrap6" data-answer-single="3">
                <button type="button" class="seg1"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg2 selected"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg3"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg4"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg5"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg6"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
              <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap wrap12" data-answer-single="8">
                <button type="button" class="seg1"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg2"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg3"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg4"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg5"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg6"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg7"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg8"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg9 selected"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg10"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg11"></button>
                <button type="button" class="seg12"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bottom">
            크기가 같은 분수는&nbsp;
            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(3)" text-align="center" placeholder="분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2)"></math-field>
            </div>
            와/과&nbsp;
            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="(8)/(12)" text-align="center" placeholder="분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2)"></math-field>
            </div>
            입니다.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </div>
                는 전체를 똑같이 3으로 나눈 것 중의 2만큼,
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>6</span>
                </div>
                은 전체를 똑같이 6으로 나눈 것 중의 3만큼,
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
                은 전체를 똑같이 12로 나눈 것 중의 8만큼 색칠합니다.
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </div>
                와&nbsp;
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
                의 색칠한 부분의 크기가 같으므로 크기가 같은 분수는
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </div>
                와&nbsp;
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
                입니다.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
